@echo off\nREM Kubernetes Deployment Script for Windows\nREM Purpose: Deploy Medicine Stock application to Kubernetes\n\nsetlocal enabledelayedexpansion\n\necho ================================================\necho   Kubernetes Deployment - Medicine Stock API\necho ================================================\necho.\n\nREM Get k8s directory\nset \"K8S_DIR=%~dp0..\\k8s\"\ncd /d \"%K8S_DIR%\"\n\necho Working directory: %K8S_DIR%\necho.\n\nREM Check prerequisites\necho [INFO] Checking prerequisites...\n\nwhere kubectl >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] kubectl not found. Please install kubectl.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\nkubectl cluster-info >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Cannot connect to Kubernetes cluster.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\nkubectl get namespace medicine-stock >nul 2>nul\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [WARN] Namespace medicine-stock not found.\n    echo [INFO] Please run Terraform (Phase 3) first.\n    exit /b 1\n)\n\necho [INFO] Prerequisites met\necho.\n\nREM Apply manifests\necho [INFO] Applying Kubernetes manifests...\n\necho [INFO] 1. Applying deployment.yaml...\nkubectl apply -f deployment.yaml\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Failed to apply deployment\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO]    Deployment created/updated\n\necho [INFO] 2. Applying service.yaml...\nkubectl apply -f service.yaml\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Failed to apply service\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO]    Service created/updated\n\necho.\n\nREM Wait for rollout\necho [INFO] Waiting for deployment rollout...\nkubectl rollout status deployment/medicine-stock -n medicine-stock --timeout=5m\nif %ERRORLEVEL% NEQ 0 (\n    echo [ERROR] Deployment rollout failed\n    exit /b 1\n)\necho [INFO] Deployment rollout successful\n\necho.\n\nREM Display status\necho [INFO] Deployment Status:\necho.\nkubectl get deployment medicine-stock -n medicine-stock\necho.\n\necho [INFO] Pod Status:\nkubectl get pods -n medicine-stock -l app=medicine-stock\necho.\n\necho [INFO] Service Status:\nkubectl get svc medicine-stock-service -n medicine-stock\necho.\n\necho ================================================\necho [INFO] Kubernetes Deployment Complete\necho ================================================\necho.\necho Next steps:\necho 1. Check logs:    kubectl logs -f deployment/medicine-stock -n medicine-stock\necho 2. Port-forward:  kubectl port-forward svc/medicine-stock-service 5000:5000 -n medicine-stock\necho 3. Test API:      curl http://localhost:5000/\necho 4. Scale pods:    kubectl scale deployment medicine-stock --replicas=3 -n medicine-stock\necho.\npause\n"